definitions.Wu3 chang2: Wuchang county level city in Harbin 哈爾濱|哈尔滨, Heilongjiang;
definitions.wu3 chang2: five constant virtues of Confucianism, namely: benevolence 仁, righteousness 義|义, propriety 禮|礼, wisdom 智 and fidelity 信; five cardinal relationships of Confucianism (between ruler and subject, father and son, husband and wife, brothers, friends); five phases of Chinese philosophy: water 水, fire 火, wood 木, metal 金, earth 土;
